high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove, turn right and face the counter.
Pick up the kettle to the right of the plate.
Walk over to the sink on the right.
Put the kettle in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it up.
Face the cabinet below the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the door, put the kettle in the cabinet on the right front edge, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To rinse a kettle and put it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the stove, then turn right to face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the kettle near the back of the counter.
Turn right, step forward, then turn left to face the sink
place the kettle in the sink, turn on the water for a few seconds, then turn off the water. pick up the kettle.
turn around, step forward, turn right, step forward, then turn right to face the kitchen counter.
Open the bottom left cabinet door, place the kettle inside, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Wash the kettle and put away in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right to walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the teapot from the counter.
Turn right to walk to the sink.
Rinse the teapot in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to face the cabinet to the left of and under the sink.
Place the teapot in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Wash a teapot to put it away in a cabinet.
